snippet.title: FOAD Pre Alpha Gameplay Preview
snippet.description:
Welcome to our first look at the pre-alpha footage of our upcoming indie game FOAD, built on Unreal Engine 5.

Here is a sneak peek of the world and gameplay mechanics we're developing for our new game. While this is still very early footage, we're excited to give you a glimpse of what we have in store.
